SUMMARY:🎶 Music Bingo at Ponysaurus 🍻
DESCRIPTION:Discover Durham Together\nCome hang with us for a fun\, low-pr
 essure night out at Ponysaurus Brewing for Music Bingo — good drinks\, g
 ood people\, and just enough friendly competition to keep things interesti
 ng.\n\nWe’ll grab a spot\, settle in\, and play along through multiple r
 ounds of bingo while songs play throughout the night. You do not need to b
 e a music expert to have a good time — half the fun is guessing\, laughi
 ng\, singing along badly\, and seeing who somehow gets lucky. And yes\, th
 ere are usually multiple chances to win\, so feel free to jump in even if 
 you show up a little later.\n\nPonysaurus is one of the best casual hang s
 pots in Durham\, so even if bingo isn’t your life’s calling\, it’s s
 till a great excuse to come out\, have a drink\, meet new people\, and enj
 oy the patio vibes. Think easy conversation\, laid-back energy\, and a nig
 ht that feels social without being forced.\n\nWhat to expect:\n🍺 Great 
 beer and a relaxed brewery vibe\n🎵 Multiple rounds of Music Bingo\n😌
  Casual\, easygoing atmosphere\n🗣️ Plenty of time to mingle between r
 ounds\n🌙 A solid weeknight excuse to get out of the house\n\nCome for t
 he bingo\, stay for the hangs.
