SUMMARY:🍻 Beers After Buehler 🌲
DESCRIPTION:Discover Durham Together\n[Moving to 4/12 next week due to rai
 n] Join us Sunday for Beers After Buehler — a laid-back social meetup wi
 th a little movement\, a little nature\, and a well-earned drink at the en
 d.\n\nWe’ll kick things off with the Al Buehler Trail\, a scenic ~3-mile
  / 5K loop around the Duke golf course area\, perfect for an easy group wa
 lk\, good conversation\, and a little Sunday reset. The trail loops around
  the course and nearby woods\, making it a great excuse to get outside bef
 ore we shift into hangout mode. ￼\n\nAfter the walk\, we’ll make the s
 hort stroll over to Bull Durham Bar at the Washington Duke Inn for drinks 
 on the patio\, where you can kick back and enjoy views of the golf course 
 with the group. Think fresh air\, relaxed vibes\, and a beer that feels a 
 little more earned than usual. ￼\n\nWhat to expect:\n🥾 Casual 3-mile 
 loop\n🍺 Drinks after at Bull Durham Bar\n🌿 Easygoing pace\, social v
 ibe\n⛳ Patio views overlooking the course\n😎 Good company\, no pressu
 re\n\nCome for the walk\, stay for the patio beers.
