SUMMARY:🍻 Beers After Buehler 🌲
DESCRIPTION:Discover Durham Together\nJoin us for: Sunday for Beers After 
 Buehler — a laid-back social meetup with a little movement\, a little na
 ture\, and a well-earned drink at the end.\n\nWe’ll kick things off with
  the Al Buehler Trail\, a scenic ~3-mile / 5K loop around the Duke golf co
 urse area\, perfect for an easy group walk\, good conversation\, and a lit
 tle Sunday reset. The trail loops around the course and nearby woods\, mak
 ing it a great excuse to get outside before we shift into hangout mode. 
 ￼\n\nAfter the walk\, we’ll make the short stroll over to Bull Durham 
 Bar at the Washington Duke Inn for drinks on the patio\, where you can kic
 k back and enjoy views of the golf course with the group. Think fresh air\
 , relaxed vibes\, and a beer that feels a little more earned than usual. 
 ￼\n\nWhat to expect:\n🥾 Casual 3-mile loop\n🍺 Drinks after at Bull
  Durham Bar\n🌿 Easygoing pace\, social vibe\n⛳ Patio views overlookin
 g the course\n😎 Good company\, no pressure\n\nCome for the walk\, stay 
 for the patio beers.
