SUMMARY:💃 The Devine Feminine Comedy Night 🎤
DESCRIPTION:Discover Durham Together\nJoin us for a fun night out at Devin
 e’s Grill & Sports Bar for a comedy showcase featuring lady comics bring
 ing the laughs\, the chaos\, and the kind of sharp observations that hit a
  little too close to home.\n\nThis one’s all about kicking back\, grabbi
 ng a drink\, and enjoying a lineup of funny women doing what they do best.
  Expect a lively\, welcoming atmosphere\, a room full of energy\, and a sh
 ow that feels a little more personal\, playful\, and unpredictable than yo
 ur average night out.\n\nWhether you’re coming for the comedy\, the drin
 ks\, or just looking for a reason to get out of the house and be around go
 od people\, this is an easy one to say yes to. It’s a great chance to su
 pport local comics\, hang with the group\, and enjoy a night that’s equa
 l parts social and entertaining.\n\nWhat to expect:\n🍸 Drinks and bar b
 ites at Devine’s\n🎤 A showcase lineup featuring women comics\n😂 A 
 fun\, casual comedy-night crowd\n✨ Easy social vibes before and after th
 e show\n🌙 A laid-back Durham night out with personality\n\nCome laugh\,
  hang out\, and support a killer lineup of women in comedy.
